snippet.title: The Sims™ 4 Star Wars™: Journey to Batuu | Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Three factions await your Sim’s arrival in The Sims™ 4 Star Wars™: Journey to Batuu Game Pack*, available on September 8! Learn more here: http://x.ea.com/64000.

Whether you join up with the Resistance, fall in with the scoundrels, or enlist with the First Order, you’ll tip the balance of power. Undertake special missions to unlock rewards and work upward through your faction’s ranks. Progress far enough, and you might actually meet Vi Moradi and Rey, Hondo Ohnaka, or Lt. Agnon and Kylo Ren. Just don’t forget your trusty droid or your customized lightsaber! 

Available September 8, 2020, on PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, and PlayStation®4.

Learn more about this Game Pack: http://x.ea.com/64002.

*REQUIRES THE SIMS 4 (SOLD SEPARATELY) AND ALL GAME UPDATES. FOR PC, SEE MINIMUM SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS FOR THE PACK.
